transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Hello
Customer: Haan ji sir aapne 9696 pe call kiya tha?
Executive: Nahi sir wo kya hai ye ladka ghol raha tha to maine ki wo check kar raha tha usne call kar diya bas.
Customer: Achcha achcha. Haan wo contact aata hai na to us pe call kar diya usne mere. To wo bhi hamare haan hamare paas bhi wo call aati hai actually. Jab aap us pe bhi kam man lijiye hum jab respond nahi karte hain tab aapko uske liye wo hai ki wo bhi aati hai. Aapka ek ticket khul gaya hai sir to isko main close kar doon?
Customer: Kaun sa ticket? Matlab us pe 9696 pe aapne call kiya tha to is pe ek ticket open ho gayi hai sir.
Executive: Isko close kar do koi dikkat nahi.
Customer: Theek hai theek hai. To aapko us pe mail pe abhi main bhej raha hoon closure to us pe please usko closure ke liye dal dijiyega. Theek hai? Haan mail pe main dal raha hoon. Baki maine jo bheja hua tha sir details aapne dekha sir? Kuch bataya nahi aapne sir revert nahi kiya.
Executive: Sir jab permanent ho tabhi to karwaye.
Customer: Haan haan. Nahi Rajasthan Stone Works to I think sir kaam mil raha hai aapko kaafi achcha is vajah se abhi aap.
Executive: Chaliye koi nahi sir karte isi mein kijiye. Jab ho jaye waise bhi leads vagaira bhi jo bhi aur bhi abhi main aapko kuch keywords WhatsApp pe dale the aapne add karaye hain usko?
Customer: Haan karwaya.
Executive: Haan us pe karwaiye ki aur bhi kuch hota hai to main aur bhi share kar dunga aapko, theek hai?
Customer: Theek hai.
Executive: Theek hai. Abhi dekhiye chaliye abhi main mail aapko kar raha hoon iska. Ek minute.
Executive: Ek minute dijiye main aapko mail kar raha hoon.
Executive: Dekhiye sir check kijiye ek mail aaya hoga.
Customer: Nahi aaya sir abhi to.
Executive: Kaun se mail pe aayega? Om Stone Art pe aayega?
Customer: Haan haan Om Stone pe Singh Saini jo. Singh Saini. Ek minute ek minute.
Executive: Nahi aaya sir.
Executive: 1:07 pe jarur aaya tha.
Customer: Chalo aate hi main karta hoon sir hai na.
Executive: Haan ji ek minute bhej raha hoon ruk jaiye.
Executive: Main is pe hai aapka. Baki chijen theek hain aapki mapping vagaira maine wahi dekh sara check kar raha tha D rank aapka ek hai. Ek product hai sir aapka D rank. Like Sandstone block isme dealing hai kya?
Customer: Nahi nahi isko delete kar dijiye.
Executive: Isme nahi deal hai to isko edit mein add na kare sir. Haan isko nahi kare. Theek hai. Baki calls inquiry vagaira aa rahi hain aapke paas theek hai. Thode abhi to teen aayi hain.
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Calls last month mein thodi thi. Buyleads pe active hain aap. New leads ka ja raha hai.
Executive: Ye jo aapka mail ID hai sir. Om Stone Art 7062. MIEN. Isi pe aaya hoga dekhiye. Is pe click pe karna hai sir?
Executive: Dekhiye aaya hoga usi pe. Main bhej raha hoon ek minute bhej raha hoon aapko. Please us pe satisfied aur okay kar dijiyega aapka close ho jayega ye.
summary:

- Customer says he has not received the mail.

- Customer wants to close the ticket.

- Customer wants to delete sandstone block from edit list.



Resolution:

- Executive agreed to close the ticket.

- Executive confirmed to send the mail again.

- Executive agreed to remove sandstone block from edit list.

None
